OL,3,CEnvironmentalists call for ban on
OL,4,Csingle use plastics by businesses on
OL,5,Cthe River
OL,7,FAn environmental group is calling for
OL,8,Fsingle use plastic cups to be phased
OL,9,Fout in venues along the Thames.
OL,11,FIn the Drink UK are part of a wider
OL,12,Fgroup who spoke to 250 pubs and bars
OL,13,Falong the River Thames over 18 months
OL,14,Fto find out how many are still using
OL,15,Fsingle use items.
OL,17,FThe research found 69% of venues are
OL,18,Fstill using single use plastic cups -
OL,19,Fmany of which end up in the river
OL,20,Fadding to problems of long-term
OL,21,Fplastic pollution.
