OL,7,FDirector of In The Drink UK, Flora
OL,8,FBlathwayt, said: "They're
OL,9,Feverywhere...there's tonnes and tonnes
OL,10,Fof plastic in the Thames, but plastic
OL,11,Fcups is something you can easily
OL,12,Fidentify.
OL,14,F"If we can just stop a proportion of
OL,15,Fthat at its source (it) will mean that
OL,16,Fwe're not having to clear up so many.
OL,17,FAnd all of the fish and the wildlife
OL,18,Fhopefully are going to be that much
OL,19,Fmore protected."
