OL,7,FThe Port of London Authority supports
OL,8,Fthe idea as part of its Clean Thames
OL,9,FPlan which aims to address all forms
OL,10,Fof pollution in the waterway,
OL,11,Fincluding these cups.
OL,13,FEmily McLean, a senior advisor at the
OL,14,FPLA, explained: "Tackling pollution is
OL,15,Fone of our key priorities and
OL,16,Fparticularly the impact of plastics
OL,17,Fand microplastics in the river is
OL,18,Freally prevalent.
