OL,7,F"We remove litter from the river every
OL,8,Fyear up to 200 tonnes, which is
OL,9,Fequivalent of about 250 family cars.
OL,11,F"The majority of that is single use
OL,12,Fplastic cups and bottles."
OL,14,FMoreover, since 2018, more than 13,500
OL,15,Fsingle use plastic cups have been
OL,16,Fcollected by Thames21 - a charity that
OL,17,Fworks with communities to restore and
OL,18,Flook after rivers, water and nature
OL,19,Facross London and the Thames Basin.
