OL,7,F"So it's really important that we
OL,8,Fcontinue to improve it for the
OL,9,Fenvironment and for everyone that
OL,10,Fwants to live and enjoy the river as
OL,11,Fwell," she continued.
OL,13,FThe report calls for some key
OL,14,Frecommendations:
OL,16,F A two-year phase-out of single-use
OL,17,Fplastic cups in licensed venues
OL,19,F A national ban on free branded
OL,20,Fsingle-use plastic cups often given
OL,21,Faway at events
